name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: AGoT LCG 2nd Ed. tournament sheet printer

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Print tournament sheets from deck lists on thronesdb.com, using the service on http://agot.temporaryna.me.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Adds a Print button to the http://thronesdb.com
deck pages to print the card list on the tournament sheet.
It uses the web service at http://agot.temporaryna.me for the printing.
